snippet.textDisplay:
And maybe the Gen Z won’t understand why tears fall from my eyes when this song plays… but for me, it’s not just music, it’s a doorway to my childhood. Every note carries memories, every lyric stretches deep into my soul. Faces of old friends, moments of laughter, stories of journeys we once walked together—all come rushing back.

One of my dearest friends 💖—we used to sing this song side by side, looking into each other’s eyes 💞, and in those moments, time stood still. Listening to it now, it feels like we’re falling back into the past, into that innocent love, that pure bond. Truly, this song is not just heard… it’s felt.


23rd September 2025❤
